{
  "name": "SlicerCache",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.Workbook\">Workbook</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.SlicerCaches\">SlicerCaches</a></strong> 属性可访问工作簿中 <strong>SlicerCache</strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n<p>每个切片器都有一个基 <strong>SlicerCache</strong> 对象，该对象表示在切片器中显示的项目，以及与对应的项目标题一起显示的平铺的当前用户界面状态。用户在 ET 中看到的每个切片器控件由带有关联的 <strong>SlicerCache</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Slicer\">Slicer</a></strong> 对象表示。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作簿上添加新的切片器缓存，并在工作表 Sheet2 中创建切片器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtTable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCaches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>2(pvtTable, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Slicer_name&quot;</span>)\n    sliCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet2&quot;</span>), <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Name&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上所有切片器缓存的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCaches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示切片器的当前筛选状态，以及有关切片器连接到哪个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PivotCache/PivotCache .htm#PivotCache.PivotCache\">PivotCache</a></strong> 或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/WorkbookConnection/WorkbookConnection .htm#WorkbookConnection.WorkbookConnection\">WorkbookConnection</a></strong> 的信息。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "CrossFilterType",
      "summary": "<p>如果多个切片器与同一数据透视表关联，那么默认情况下，如果在一个切片器中作为筛选依据的项目在另一个切片器中没有对应的数据，那么这些项目将灰显。例如，如果有 Country 切片器和 State 切片器，您单击 Country 切片器中的某个国家/地区，那么不属于该国家/地区的所有州将灰显。此功能称为“交叉筛选”。</p>\n<p>对应于 <strong>CrossFilterType</strong> 属性设置的用户界面设置是 <strong>“切片器设置”</strong> 对话框中的 <strong>“直观地指示空数据项”</strong> 和 <strong>“最后显示空数据项”</strong> 复选框。将 <strong>CrossFilterType</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>xlSlicerCrossFilterShowItemsWithDataAtTop</strong> 对应于同时选中 <strong>“直观地指示空数据项”</strong> 和 <strong>“最后显示空数据项”</strong> 复选框。将 <strong>CrossFilterType</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>xlSlicerCrossFilterShowItemsWithNoData</strong> 对应于只选中 <strong>“直观地指示空数据项”</strong> 复选框。同时清除这两个复选框对应于将 <strong>CrossFilterType</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>xlSlicerNoCrossFilter</strong>。</p>\n<p><strong>SlicerCache</strong> 对象的 <strong>CrossFilterType</strong> 属性不支持 OLAP 数据源 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>OLAP</strong> = <strong>True</strong>)。对于 OLAP 数据源，应改用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerCacheLevel\">SlicerCacheLevel</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.CrossFilterType\">CrossFilterType</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置切片器是否与共享同一切片器缓存的其他切片器一起参与交叉筛选，以及如何显示交叉筛选。可读/写</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_name”的切片器缓存使用的交叉筛选的类型及其可视化方式是否为 xlSlicerCrossFilterShowItemsWithDataAtTop。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CrossFilterType</span> == xlSlicerCrossFilterShowItemsWithDataAtTop)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿上第一个切片器缓存使用的交叉筛选的类型及其可视化方式设置为 xlSlicerCrossFilterShowItemsWithNoData。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sliCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CrossFilterType</span> = xlSlicerCrossFilterShowItemsWithNoData\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSlicerCrossFilterType 枚举.html\">XlSlicerCrossFilterType</a></strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "FilterCleared",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回是否清除切片器或时间线筛选器状态。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_name”的切片器缓存是否清除切片器筛选器状态。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FilterCleared</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿第三个切片器缓存是否清除切片器筛选器状态。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FilterCleared</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Index",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCaches/SlicerCaches .htm#SlicerCaches.SlicerCaches\">SlicerCaches</a></strong> 集合中指定 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SlicerCache\">SlicerCache</a></strong> 对象的索引。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿“切片器_name”切片器缓存的索引号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作簿中切片器缓存“切片器_date”的索引号为2，则清除该切片器缓存的筛选器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_date&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>) {\n        slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearManualFilter</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "List",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果切片器缓存适用于表上的切片器，则为 <strong>True</strong>；否则为 <strong>False</strong>。 只读 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_name”的切片器缓存是否适用于表上的切片器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">List</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一张工作簿第二个切片器缓存是否适用于表上的切片器，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (slCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">List</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器缓存适用于表上的切片器&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器缓存不适用于表上的切片器&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "<p>切片器缓存的名称在工作簿命名空间中必须是唯一的。默认情况下，分配给切片器缓存的名称是 <code>Slicer_</code> 后跟与该切片器缓存关联的数据透视表字段的名称。例如，如果切片器与数据透视表中的“Product Category”字段关联，则默认名称为 <code>Slicer_Product_Category</code>（字段名中的任何空格替换为下划线字符）。如果同一工作簿中有多个“Product Category”字段与某个切片器关联，或者工作簿中有某个其他命名实体也名为 <code>Slicer_Product_Category</code>，那么 ET 将在该名称后面附加一个编号来产生唯一名称，如 <code>Slicer_Product_Category1</code>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置切片器缓存的名称。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿第一个切片器缓存的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作簿第三个切片器缓存的名称并显示。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_nameid&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "OLAP",
      "summary": "<p>如果切片器是基于 OLAP 数据源，则为 <strong>True</strong>；否则为 <strong>False</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回与指定的切片器缓存关联的切片器是否基于 OLAP 数据源。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿第二个切片器缓存关联的切片器是否基于 OLAP 数据源。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLAP</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作簿中名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存关联的切片器未基于 OLAP 数据源，则删除该切片器缓存。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLAP</span> == <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>) {\n        slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "PivotTables",
      "summary": "<p>如果与指定的 <strong>SlicerCache</strong> 关联的切片器未连接到任何数据透视表，那么 <strong>PivotTables</strong> 属性返回的 <strong>SlicerPivotTables</strong> 集合将为空。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerPivotTables/SlicerPivotTables .htm#SlicerPivotTables.SlicerPivotTables\">SlicerPivotTables</a></strong> 集合，其中包含有关切片器缓存当前正在筛���的数据透视表的信息。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿第一个切片器缓存正在筛选的第一张数据透视表的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtTables = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTables</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(pvtTables.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿中名为“切片器_date”的切片器缓存正在筛选的第一张数据透视表的字段的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtTables = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_date&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTables</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(pvtTables.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "SlicerPivotTables",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "ShowAllItems",
      "summary": "<p>当 <strong>ShowAllItems</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>True</strong>（默认）时，已从源数据中删除的项将在连接到指定切片器缓存的切片器中显示。<strong>ShowAllItems</strong> 属性对应于 <strong>“切片器设置”</strong> 对话框中的 <strong>“显示从数据源删除的项目”</strong> 复选框的设置。</p>\n<p><strong>ShowAllItems</strong> 属性只适用于基于工作簿区域或列表的切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>SourceType</strong> = <strong>xlDatabase</strong>) 或基于关系数据源的切片器（<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>SourceType</strong> = <strong>xlExternal</strong> 且 <strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.OLAP\">OLAP</a></strong> = <strong>False</strong>）。如果切片器连接到基于外部 OLAP 数据源的数据透视表 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>OLAP</strong> = <strong>True</strong>)，那么尝试对该切片器设置 <strong>ShowAllItems</strong> 属性将生成运行时错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置连接到指定切片器缓存的切片器是否显示已从对应的透视缓存中删除的项。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿第二个切片器缓存关联的切片器是否显示已从对应的透视缓存中删除的项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShowAllItems</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿中名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存关联的切片器设置为不显示已从对应的透视缓存中删除的项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>)\n    slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShowAllItems</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "SlicerCacheType",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器缓存的类型：切片器 (xlSlicer) 或时间线 (xlTimeline) 。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿第二个切片器缓存的类型是否为 xlSlicer。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCacheType</span> == xlSlicer)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一张工作簿中名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存的类型，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">switch</span> (slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCacheType</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlSlicer</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器缓存类型为切片器&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">xlTimeline</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器缓存类型为时间线&quot;</span>)\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSlicerCacheType 枚举.html\">XlSlicerCacheType</a></p>\n",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "SlicerItems",
      "summary": "<p><strong>SlicerCache</strong> 对象的 <strong>SlicerItems</strong> 属性只适用于基于数据透视表，且该数据透视表又基于工作簿区域或列表的切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>SourceType</strong> = <strong>xlDatabase</strong>)，或基于数据透视表，且该数据透视表又基于关系数据源的切片器（<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>SourceType</strong> = <strong>xlExternal</strong> 且 <strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.OLAP\">OLAP</a></strong> = <strong>False</strong>）。对于连接到外部 OLAP 数据源的切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>OLAP</strong> = <strong>True</strong>)，如果试图访问其 <strong>SlicerItems</strong> 属性，将会生成运行时错误。对于 OLAP 数据源，请改用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerCacheLevel\">SlicerCacheLevel</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerItems\">SlicerItems</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerItems/SlicerItems .htm#SlicerItems.SlicerItems\">SlicerItems</a></strong> 集合，该集合包含切片器缓存中所有项的集合。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿第一个切片器缓存中项的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例取消选择第一张工作簿上名为“切片器_name”的切片器缓存的第三项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicerItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    slicerItem.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selected</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "SlicerItems",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Slicers",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicers/Slicers .htm#Slicers.Slicers\">Slicers</a></strong> 集合，其中包含与指定的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SlicerCache\">SlicerCache</a></strong> 关联的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Slicer\">Slicer</a></strong> 对象的集合。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一个切片器缓存中第一个切片器的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Slicers</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名��“切片器_id”的切片器缓存中第一个切片器的高度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Slicers</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Slicers",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "SortItems",
      "summary": "<p>此属性的默认设置为 <strong>xlSlicerSortAscending</strong>。</p>\n<p><strong>SlicerCache</strong> 对象的 <strong>SortItems</strong> 属性只适用于基于连接到工作簿区域或列表的数据透视表的切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>SourceType</strong> = <strong>xlDatabase</strong>)。对于连接到 OLAP 数据源的切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.OLAP\">OLAP</a></strong> = <strong>True</strong>)，如果试图访问其 <strong>SortItems</strong> 属性，那么将生成运行时错误。对于 OLAP 数据源，请改用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerCacheLevel\">SlicerCacheLevel</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SortItems\">SortItems</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置是否对切片器中的项排序。可读/写</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_name”的切片器缓存中项的排序顺序是否为 xlSlicerSortAscending。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortItems</span> == xlSlicerSortAscending)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿上名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存中项的排序顺序设置为 xlSlicerSortDescending。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>)\n    slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortItems</span> = xlSlicerSortDescending\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSlicerSort 枚举.html\">XlSlicerSort</a></strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "SortUsingCustomLists",
      "summary": "<p><strong>SortUsingCustomLists</strong> 属性对应于 <strong>­“切片器设置”</strong> 对话框的 <strong>“排序时使用自定义列表”</strong> 复选框的设置。若要访问与当前安装的 ET 关联的自定义列表，请依次单击 <strong>“文件”</strong> 选项卡、<strong>“选项”</strong>、<strong>“高级”</strong>，然后单击 <strong>“常规”</strong> 类别下的 <strong>“编辑自定义列表”</strong>。</p>\n<p><strong>SortUsingCustomLists</strong> 属性只适用于筛选非 OLAP 数据源的切片器。试图从筛选 OLAP 数据源的切片器缓存 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.OLAP\">OLAP</a></strong> = <strong>True</strong>) 访问此属性，将生成运行时错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定切片器缓存中的项是否将按自定义列表排序。可读/写</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_age”的切片器缓存中的项是否按自定义列表排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_age&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortUsingCustomLists</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿上第一个切片器缓存中的项设置为不按自定义列表排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortUsingCustomLists</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "SourceName",
      "summary": "<p>对于基于工作簿数据的切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SourceType\">SourceType</a></strong> = <strong>xlDatabase</strong>) 或基于非 OLAP 外部数据的切片器（<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>SourceType</strong> = <strong>xlExternal</strong> 且 <strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.OLAP\">OLAP</a></strong> = <strong>False</strong>），则返回源数据中相应列的名称。</p>\n<p>对于 OLAP 切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>OLAP</strong> = <strong>True</strong>)，则返回切片器所基于的层次结构的 MDX 唯一名称。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器所连接到的数据源的名称。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存所连接到的数据源的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceName</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿上第一个切片器缓存所连接到的数据源的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`数据源名称：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${slcCache.SourceName}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "SourceType",
      "summary": "<p>只支持 <strong>xlDatabase</strong> 和 <strong>xlExternal</strong> 数据源类型。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器所连接到的数据源的类型。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存所连接到的数据源的类型是否为 xlDatabase。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceType</span> == xlDatabase)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一张工作簿上第二个切片器缓存所连接到的数据源的类型是否为xlPivotTable，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceType</span> == xlPivotTable) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;数据源的类型是 xlPivotTable&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;数据源的类型不是 xlPivotTable&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlPivotTableSourceType 枚举.html\">XlPivotTableSourceType</a></p>\n",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "VisibleSlicerItems",
      "summary": "<p><strong>VisibleSlicerItems</strong> 属性只适用于基于数据透视表，且该数据透视表又基于工作簿区域或列表的切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>SourceType</strong> = <strong>xlDatabase</strong>)。对于连接到 OLAP 数据源的切片器 (<strong>SlicerCache</strong>.<strong>OLAP</strong> = <strong>True</strong>)，如果试图访问其 <strong>VisibleSlicerItems</strong> 属性，将会生成运行时错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerItems/SlicerItems .htm#SlicerItems.SlicerItems\">SlicerItems</a></strong> 集合，该集合包含指定的切片器缓存中所有可见项的集合。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_score”的切片器缓存可见项的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_score&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">VisibleSlicerItems</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿上第一个切片器缓存的可见项集合的第一项的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> vsScItems = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">VisibleSlicerItems</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(vsScItems.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "SlicerItems",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "ClearAllFilters",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>清除切片器或时间线的筛选器，具体取决于切片器缓存类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除活动工作簿上所有切片器缓存的筛选器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCaches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearAllFilters</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除第一张工作簿中名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存的筛选器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearAllFilters</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "ClearDateFilter",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>清除时间线的筛选器 (日期筛选器) 。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除第一张工作簿中第二个切片器缓存的日期筛选器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearDateFilter</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除活动工作簿中名为“切片器_id”切片器缓存的日期筛选器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearDateFilter</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "ClearManualFilter",
      "summary": "<p>如果使用 <strong>ClearManualFilter</strong> 方法从一个切片器中清除筛选，但是有一个或多个切片器正交叉筛选该切片器中的数据，那么第一个切片器中的某些项将保持为淡灰。例如，如果有交叉筛选的 Customer 和 Country 切片器，并且您执行 <code>ActiveWorkbook.SlicerCaches(&quot;Slicer_Customer&quot;).ClearManualFilter()</code>，那么 Customer 切片器中的所有项要在您执行 <code>ActiveWorkbook.SlicerCaches(&quot;Slicer_Country&quot;).ClearManualFilter()</code> 后才会变得可用。有关交叉筛选的详细信息，请参阅 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.CrossFilterType\">CrossFilterType</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>清除与指定的切片器缓存关联的所有切片器的筛选。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除活动工作簿上所有切片器缓存的筛选器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCaches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearManualFilter</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除第一张工作簿中第三个切片器缓存的筛选器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearManualFilter</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "<p>若要脱离切片器缓存，而单独删除一个特定的切片器，那么应改用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Slicer\">Slicer</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Delete\">Delete</a></strong> 方法。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>删除指定的切片器缓存及其关联的切片器。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作簿“切片器_name”切片器缓存，以及与该切片器缓存关联的“name”切片器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作簿中第二个切片器缓存的名称为“切片器_date”，则删除该切片器缓存及关联的切片器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slcCache = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_date&quot;</span>) {\n        slcCache.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
